      </div>

      <div class="col-3">
        <pre><code class="language-css font-sans-serif">.font-sans-serif</code></pre>
      </div>

    </div>

  </div>

  <div class="col-12">

    <h3 class="heading heading--small">Resets</h3>

    <div class="grid">

      <div class="col-3">
        <pre><code class="language-css lh-normal no-margin">.no-margin</code></pre>
      </div>

      <div class="col-3">
        <pre><code class="language-css fw-strong no-border">.no-border</code></pre>
      </div>

    </div>

  </div>

  <hr />

  <div class="col-12">

    <h3 class="heading heading--large">Layout</h3>
    <p>This site use <a href="http://gridlex.devlint.fr/">Gridlex</a> for flexbox based layout, in a 12 column grid.</p>
    <pre><code class="language-html">&lt;div class="grid"&gt;
  &lt;div class="col-6_sm-12"&gt;
    &lt;p&gt;Quick example of concept.&lt;/p&gt;
  &lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;</code></pre>

  </div>

  <hr />

  <div class="col-12">

    <h3 class="heading heading--large">Variables</h3>
    <p>Some important site specific variables are:</p>

    <pre><code class="language-scss">$speed: .25s;
$margin: 1rem;
$margin-sm: 0.5rem;</code></pre>

  </div>

</div>


